comment: This class wasn't too difficult. Took a lot of my time to complete the assignments (5 total). Two exams. I don't recommend the text because it's just a bunch of case studies that you go over in class. I highly recommend you going to class or you won't pass (seriously). Take notes! He's very intelligent and not as bad as people lead on. Great guy.
If it wasn't for attendance I would not come because his lecture notes are useless

This was a difficult class, but very much worth it. I worked to get my A in this class, but I loved every minute of it. Definitely a class you will want to take with Dr. Leite. He was a great professor.
